<h4>Quick start for Review search</h4>
<p/>Enter a number (N) into the search field and press Enter or click Search.  This will show you records created or updated in the last N days.
<p/> E.g.  <%= link_to('5', search_path(query_string: '5', query_target: 'review'),class:'blue',title:"Run the described search.") %>
<br>
<p/>Start any search with <q>count</q> to change it from a list search to a count search.
<p/> E.g.  <%= link_to('count 5', search_path(query_string: 'count 5', query_target: 'review'),class:'blue',title:"Run the described search.") %>
